随着疫情席卷全球，《死亡搁浅》在欧美玩家里的评价开始上升。
As the epidemic engulfed the world, "Death Grounding" in the United States and Europe at home began to rise.
南回归线。
Tropic of Cancer.
趣闻。
Interesting news.
2天前。
Two days ago.
岛哥哥什么时候骗过你？。
When did the island brother cheat you?
发售后很长一段时间里，《死亡搁浅》都可以说是一款“不是零分就是满分”的游戏——电波对得上的玩家对其穷尽赞美之辞，对不上得则恨不得把它埋进坟堆，这么说并不夸张。
It's no exaggeration to say that "Death Grounding" is a "zero or full score" game for a long time after the release - a game in which players on the airwaves pay tribute to it, rather than bury it in the grave.
。
.
小岛秀夫自己也认识到了这一点。
The islet scholar himself realized this.
早先接受媒体采访的时候，他就曾经表示：“北美玩家对FPS非常热衷，《死亡搁浅》的游戏类型对他们来说可能难以理解，这是文化差异造成的结果。
In an earlier interview with the media, he once said: "North American players are very keen on the FPS and the type of game they might find it difficult to understand because of cultural differences.
”。
"
这话说得很婉转，但“北美玩家只懂打枪”的弦外之音同样明显。
This is tactful, but the implication that "North American players only know how to shoot" is equally obvious.
不论小岛秀夫本身有没有这个意思，总之当时是激怒了一大批北美玩家。
Whether or not the isle owner meant it or not, it infuriated a large number of North American players.
。
.
那时没人知道，尚未横空出世的新冠病毒即将席卷全球。
No one knew then that the new crown virus, which had not yet been born, was about to engulf the globe.
。
.
《死亡搁浅》发售于去年的11月8日，不久之后，新冠开始在中国肆虐。
"Death Grounding" went on sale on Nov. 8, and soon after, the new crown began to wreak havoc in China.
即使在那时，大洋彼岸的人们对病毒也没什么实感——所谓的疫情好像只是手机屏幕里的一段字或是一张图。
Even then, people on the other side of the ocean had no real sense of the virus - the so-called epidemic seemed to be a word or a picture on a mobile phone screen.
。
.
直到最近，感染人数开始攀升，政府下达隔离通知，餐馆酒吧暂停营业，大街上空空荡荡时，他们才后知后觉地发现，游戏中的剧情好像成了真。
Until recently, the number of infections began to climb, the government issued quarantine notices, restaurants and bars were closed and the streets were empty before they realized that the story in the game seemed to be true.
。
.
在《死亡搁浅》中，没有实体的BT游荡在旷野，绝大部分幸存者都龟缩进城市，而玩家扮演的山姆，则需要通过送货将人类重新“连接”起来——这与当下现状似乎相差无几。
In "The Grounding of Death," BT loafs around in the wilderness, most of the survivors huddle into the city, while Sam, as the player plays, needs to "connect" humans again through delivery - a situation that seems little different from the status quo.
人们各自隔离在家中，只有快递员依然在外奔波。
People were isolated in their homes, and only couriers were still on the move.
。
.
而“预言”到这一切的小岛秀夫，很快就成为了人们心中的先知、神。
And "prophecy" to all of these island Xiufu, soon became the people's hearts of the prophets, God.
。
.
《死亡搁浅》中所有晦涩的隐喻在此刻都显得直白，因为它不再是游戏中的故事，而是无数人正经历着的生活。
All the obscure metaphors of "The Grounding of Death" seem straightforward at the moment, because it is no longer a game story, but a life that millions of people are experiencing.
对于这款慢热的游戏，小岛秀夫曾自信地表示，时间会证明一切。
For this slow-hot game, the islet Xiufu has confidently said that time will prove everything.
到如今，再坚持无神论的人似乎都不得不扪心自问一句：“小岛秀夫真的什么都算到了？”。
Until now, atheists seem to be forced to ask themselves: "Is it true that the islanders have arrived at everything?"
当然，小岛秀夫是不是神仙我们不知道，我们只知道，在发售数月之后的这个节点，《死亡搁浅》再次激发了人们的创作欲望。
Of course, we don't know if the isle-bearer is a faery or not, but we only know that "The Grounding of Death" has revived the urge to create something a few months after its launch.
。
.
这次疫情中，口罩是绝对的主角，出于安全卫生和狂拽酷炫的双重考虑，有人设计出了希格斯同款黄金骷髅口罩。
In this outbreak, the mask is the absolute protagonist, because of safety and hygiene and crazy drag cool dazzle double consideration, someone designed Higgs with the same gold skull mask.
。
.
不少人对遭遇疯抢，千金难买的厕纸念念不忘，这股执念也体现在他们做出来的图里。
Many people are obsessed with the problem of frantic looting and buying toilet paper, and this obsession is reflected in the way they make it.
。
.
《死亡搁浅》“预言成真”的情况下，通过对游戏的调侃，人们在紧张压抑的氛围中松了一口气。
"Death Grounding" is "predicted to be true," through the fun of the game, people in the atmosphere of tension and depression relieved.
除此之外，已经触手可及的疫情也促使他们重新将审视的目光投向中国——那里有更多的“山姆”。
Beyond that, the epidemic is already within reach, prompting a renewed focus on China, where there are more "sams."
。
.
惊叹这幅情景与《死亡搁浅》描绘的世界何其相似的同时，跨越山海的“连接”也形成了。
While marvel at how similar this scene is to the world depicted in "The Grounding of Death," a "connection" has emerged across the mountain.
Rdddit上，有人为武汉快递员送货的照片配上了《死亡搁浅》的UI。
On Rdddit, a photo of a delivery by a Wuhan courier was accompanied by the UI of Death Grounding.
。
.
下面最高赞的评论回复道：“希望前方有发电机。
The following highly complimentary comment replied: "Hopefully there will be a generator ahead.
”。
"
《死亡搁浅》中，车辆需要充电后才能使用。
In Death Grounding, a car needs to be recharged before it can be used.
